        "args": [
            {
                "$type": "array<string>",
                "$description": "Array of expression. An expression is a string that contains a comparison between two values. Example: '{Variable_Name} > 1000'. The expression can contain the following operators: >, <, >=, <=, ==, !=. First item of array is priority. If the first expression is true, the second expression will not be evaluated. Example: ['{Variable_Name} > 1000', '{Variable_Name} < 2000']",
